prompts.frontCover: A charming, cartoon-style slice of pepperoni pizza, looking slightly stressed and sweating cartoon sweat drops, is doing a yoga warrior pose. The pizza slice has googly eyes and a determined but wobbly expression. A single, mischievous pepperoni is sliding off its back. Centered below the pizza, the word "birthday" is written in a beautiful, readable, flowing handwritten cursive script. The entire scene is a flat 2D artwork in a watercolor painting style, featuring soft, warm colors, visible artistic brush strokes, a subtle paper texture background, and organic paint bleeds around the edges of the pizza and text.
